FBIS4-50162 "drchi094_k_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Chen Ziming Freed on Bail for Medical Treatment Chen Ziming Freed on Bail for Medical Treatment OW1305165994 Beijing XINHUA in English 1638 GMT 13 May 94 OW1305165994 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 13 (XINHUA) -- Chen Ziming, who had been in custody, has been released on bail for medical treatment today with the permission of Chinese judicial authorities. Chen's release according to law has been learned from Chinese judicial authorities.
